widgets_values:
1. generate a base image with the control image

- start with lanczos lanczos 1.00 strength/denoise
- if under 1 mp set to 1 mp
- describe initial control image (could help with consistency)
- gradually decrease strength until artifacts disappear
- gradually decrease denoise until artifiacts appear

2. upscale base image to 4mp
- set new base image to control
- set base upscale method to nearest exact
- decrease denoise until artifacts start to appear or if image quality trash lower strength first
- replace base image

3. upscale base image to 16mp
- remove prompt
- use special 16mp control
- set strength to 0.50 & denoise to 0.66
- decrease denoise if picture looks okay (other wise increase up to 0.80)
